{"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Appearances","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"emphasized"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"primary or high-priority information."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"muted","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Status","anchor":"Status","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication."}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Neutral","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status needs to be communicated."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Accent","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Positive","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Warning","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or contextual information."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Shape","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Shape"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"text":"Size","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Size"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags can have two sizes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Default"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Small"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Layout","type":"heading","text":"Layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"-","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Bullet","type":"text"}]},{"text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Icon","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"such as status, type, or action.","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Loader"}]},{"text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2},{"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"c